{
  "stem": "2684.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he showed me the stars, which way to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were going through bushes, unbelievable, for 25 kilometers with a daughter on the arm and about 150 people behind me all going to Austria.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And apart from us, it was about another 150,000 people who left Hungary in that time in certain different places going to Austria.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived safely, bloodied because the pricks in the-- in the bushes cut everything off-- socks, and clothes, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we arrived to Austria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and in the hotel, we got from the joint, which was the World Jewish Organization, some money in order to be able to stay in a hotel in Austria.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In those days, the revolution, the refugees was helped by every country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Australia helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "England helped, France and the United States, and everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they gave quote to certain countries, certain amount of people could go immediately without visas or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in the hotel-- actually, in Vienna, I met all my other cousins who, since then, left Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So five cousins met in a hotel and put five nations into a hat, where to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, you put your things into the hat and pick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I go to Australia because, with international football, I was in Red China.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was in Moscow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was very close to Australia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in my childhood, I read about sharks and whatever a child reads about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going to Australia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You pick whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You go wherever you wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they take the things out of the hat, and everybody decided to come to Australia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All we had to do was go to the Australian embassy and apply for coming to Australia free of charge.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
